Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}

### Create a new ToDo item
POST {{empUrl}}/todo
Authorization: Bearer {{empToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task": "Prepare daily report",
  "deadline": "2025-02-10T17:00:00"
}

